description: WINNER-BEST HEAD SHOP- ""BEST OF HOUSTON"" 2015 & 2016! Conveniently located in the Montrose area of Houston! Enjoy our HUGE selection of Vaporizers, E-Cigs, E-Juice, Smoking Accessories and Local Hand Blown Glass at great prices! We carry many brands including Illadelph, PAX, Volcano, Santa Cruz Shredder, Aspire, Kanger, Goldstein, Governmint, Pulse, Grav Labs/ Helix, Texas Tubes, Healthstone, 420 Jars, Dr. Dabber, Puff Co., PAX, JUUL and many many more. We have an awesome and always growing selection of E-Cigs, E-Juice and E-Cig accessories, with many brand names at affordable prices. We strive to help and inform our customers on getting started with a setup that is most helpful and beneficial to that particular individual! No question is a stupid question, we want you to leave with all your questions answered! We understand this is a thriving and growing industry and we try our best to be on top of all the latest and greatest products currently available. Please check us out on: Facebook: @burnsmokeshop / Twitter: @BurnHouston Instagram: @burnsmokeshop ....great pics of our glass inventory and other great products posted weekly
